# very important that the copy is named as A) or B) below
#
# A) ${HOME}/_FENSALIRCONFIG_
# B) _FENSALIR_USER_CONFIG_HOME_/_FENSALIRCONFIG_
#
# Fensalir first tries to load A) if it exists, otherwise Fensalir
# tries to load B) if it exists. If neither exist Fensalir falls back
# to using the default values as described below for each
# configuration option.
#
# Note: Your personal copy will be preserved when Fensalir is updated.
